title: Zilean MAin looking for JGL/ADC/TOP (Main,OTP)
body:
http://euw.op.gg/summoner/userName=TickingTimeBomb

Hey guys,

my name is Demos. I play mainly Zilean on the Mid lane and now I look for Duo Q partners to gain elo in ranked games.
I'm currently Plat 5 on my Zil only acc and Gold 2 on my first account, that i want to get to plat as well. The link above leads to 
the zil account.
Short sumary: 
{{champion:26}} 
Mastery Level 7
74k pts.

4.0 / 3.0 / 11.4

I look for JGL,ADC or TOP players with a small champ pool, favorite would be OTP, becaue it works much better with zilean.
Language: GER/ ENG, with discord optional.

I hope I'll see you on the Rift!
Best regards, Demos

Main acc: http://euw.op.gg/summoner/userName=D%C3%ABmos
